<plot>Inspired by the true story of Sandra Daniels, who used abuse to motivate her success. Daniels started her journey to freedom at sixteen when she was forced to live in her car. The film looks at how child abuse plagues the adult, threatening their happiness until they are willing to cut "The Ties That Bind." It's a short film is about courage. It asks, "How does one break free from a painful past and move forward to a fulfilling life?" and it finds an answer we can all live with. For more information contact: Angela Gibbs (323) 514-6281</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?596014</url></doc>
